{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.1","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:1","prev_osis_id":"Deut.023.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le divorce<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. (Mt 5:31, 32; 19:3-9.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019un homme aura pris et \u00e9pous\u00e9 une femme qui viendrait \u00e0 ne pas trouver gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 ses yeux, parce qu\u2019il a d\u00e9couvert en elle quelque chose de honteux, il \u00e9crira pour elle une lettre de divorce, et, apr\u00e8s la lui avoir remise en main, il la renverra de sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.23.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 23:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.23.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.2","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:2","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Elle sortira de chez lui, s\u2019en ira, et pourra devenir la femme d\u2019un autre homme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.3","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:3","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Si ce dernier homme la prend en aversion, \u00e9crit pour elle une lettre de divorce, et, apr\u00e8s la lui avoir remise en main, la renvoie de sa maison; ou bien, si ce dernier homme qui l\u2019a prise pour femme vient \u00e0 mourir,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.4","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:4","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>alors le premier mari qui l\u2019avait renvoy\u00e9e ne pourra pas la reprendre pour femme apr\u00e8s qu\u2019elle a \u00e9t\u00e9 souill\u00e9e, car c\u2019est une abomination devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et tu ne chargeras point de p\u00e9ch\u00e9 le pays que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te donne pour h\u00e9ritage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.5","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:5","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le nouveau mari\u00e9 exempt\u00e9 du service militaire. Les pr\u00eats sur gages. Le vol d\u2019un homme. Les l\u00e9preux<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-9: cf. De 20:7. Ex 21:16. (L\u00e9 13; 14.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019un homme sera nouvellement mari\u00e9, il n\u2019ira point \u00e0 l\u2019arm\u00e9e, et on ne lui imposera aucune charge; il sera exempt\u00e9 par raison de famille pendant un an, et il r\u00e9jouira la femme qu\u2019il a prise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.6","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:6","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>On ne prendra point pour gage les deux meules, ni la meule de dessus; car ce serait prendre pour gage la vie m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.7","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:7","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Si l\u2019on trouve un homme qui ait d\u00e9rob\u00e9 l\u2019un de ses fr\u00e8res, l\u2019un des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui en ait fait son esclave ou qui l\u2019ait vendu, ce voleur sera puni de mort. Tu \u00f4teras ainsi le mal du milieu de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.8","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:8","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Prends garde \u00e0 la plaie de la l\u00e8pre, afin de bien observer et de faire tout ce que vous enseigneront les sacrificateurs, les L\u00e9vites; vous aurez soin d\u2019agir d\u2019apr\u00e8s les ordres que je leur ai donn\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.9","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:9","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Souviens-toi de ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, fit \u00e0 Marie pendant la route, lors de votre sortie d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.10","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:10","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les mercenaires. Les droits de l\u2019\u00e9tranger, de l\u2019orphelin et de la veuve<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-18: cf. Ex 22:26, 27, 21-24. (L\u00e9 19:13. Ja 5:4. Mal 3:5.) Ps 146:7, 9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Si tu fais \u00e0 ton prochain un pr\u00eat quelconque, tu n\u2019entreras point dans sa maison pour te saisir de son gage;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.11","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:11","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>tu resteras dehors, et celui \u00e0 qui tu fais le pr\u00eat t\u2019apportera le gage dehors.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.12","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:12","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Si cet homme est pauvre, tu ne te coucheras point, en retenant son gage;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.13","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:13","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>tu le lui rendras au coucher du soleil, afin qu\u2019il couche dans son v\u00eatement et qu\u2019il te b\u00e9nisse; et cela te sera imput\u00e9 \u00e0 justice devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.14","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:14","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Tu n\u2019opprimeras point le mercenaire, pauvre et indigent, qu\u2019il soit l\u2019un de tes fr\u00e8res, ou l\u2019un des \u00e9trangers demeurant dans ton pays, dans tes portes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.15","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:15","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tu lui donneras le salaire de sa journ\u00e9e avant le coucher du soleil; car il est pauvre, et il lui tarde de le recevoir. Sans cela, il crierait \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel contre toi, et tu te chargerais d\u2019un p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.16","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:16","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>On ne fera point mourir les p\u00e8res pour les enfants, et l\u2019on ne fera point mourir les enfants pour les p\u00e8res; on fera mourir chacun pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.17","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:17","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Tu ne porteras point atteinte au droit de l\u2019\u00e9tranger et de l\u2019orphelin, et tu ne prendras point en gage le v\u00eatement de la veuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.18","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:18","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Tu te souviendras que tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 esclave en \u00c9gypte, et que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019a rachet\u00e9; c\u2019est pourquoi je te donne ces commandements \u00e0 mettre en pratique.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.19","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:19","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.020,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 19-22: cf. L\u00e9 19:9, 10. Ps 68:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Quand tu moissonneras ton champ, et que tu auras oubli\u00e9 une gerbe dans le champ, tu ne retourneras point la prendre: elle sera pour l\u2019\u00e9tranger, pour l\u2019orphelin et pour la veuve, afin que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te b\u00e9nisse dans tout le travail de tes mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.20","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:20","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Quand tu secoueras tes oliviers, tu ne cueilleras point ensuite les fruits rest\u00e9s aux branches: ils seront pour l\u2019\u00e9tranger, pour l\u2019orphelin et pour la veuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.21","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:21","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.024.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Quand tu vendangeras ta vigne, tu ne cueilleras point ensuite les grappes qui y seront rest\u00e9es: elles seront pour l\u2019\u00e9tranger, pour l\u2019orphelin et pour la veuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.22","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:22","prev_osis_id":"Deut.024.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.025.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.24.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Tu te souviendras que tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 esclave dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte; c\u2019est pourquoi je te donne ces commandements \u00e0 mettre en pratique.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.25.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.25.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.24.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.24.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb1c64e13.54495534');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1c64e13.54495534\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" st